display_long_description:
LET'S GO ON A SAFARI ADVENTURE!
Experience the adventure of a hunting expedition in the African wilderness.  Drive your off road vehicle through the dusty African bush looking for highly valuable animal trophies.  

STAY ALERT!
You're not he only hunter lurking about.  Be ready to defend yourself and your vehicle from menacing predators.  Survive until you reach the extraction point to keep your valuable trophies.

BECOME A PRO HUNTER
Sometimes being a sharp shooter isn't enough.  Upgrade your equipment to gain an edge.  Improve the performance of your weapons, vehicle, and personnel.  Complete challenges to unlock unique skins for your weapons and vehicle.

ENJOY YOUR TROPHY ROOM
Your most prized trophies are displayed in your home base to relive the experience of the hunt. 

If you enjoyed our game or want to give us some valuable feedback, join us on Facebook.
https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61561158972131
